<?php
return ['messages'=>['<h5><a href="https://eji.com.hk/stage/our-inspiring-visit-to-evangel-childrens-home/">Our Inspiring Visit to Evangel Children\'s Home</a></h5>'=>'<h5><a href="https://x4v3b03dwm-staging.onrocket.site/our-inspiring-visit-to-evangel-childrens-home/">探访播道儿童之家</a></h5>','<p><strong><big>Follow us</big></strong></p>'=>'<p><strong><big>关注我们</big></strong></p>','<p>Amidst our busy business work schedule, we never forget our responsibilities and commitment to our role as a pillar in the community. Our ongoing partnership with <a href="https://www.ech.org.hk/">Evangel Children’s Home</a> is a cornerstone of this commitment, allowing us to support and uplift some of the most vulnerable members of society – children who come from challenging backgrounds.</p>'=>'<p>即使工作繁忙，EJI团队始终不忘支援社区的承诺。 我们与<a href="https://www.ech.org.hk/">播道儿童之家</a>的长期合作是这份承诺的核心：支持社会中脆弱的群体——来自困难背景的儿童，是我们作为企业的责任。</p>','<p>On this beautiful day on June 29, after all our demanding show schedule from the first half of the year, our dedicated volunteering team had the privilege of visiting the Evangel Children’s Home - a tradition that continues to enrich both our hearts and those of the children we meet. We once again engaged in a delightful ink art painting workshop centered around the theme of <em>Love in In</em>k, <em>Sparrows and Lychee </em>(「我愛水墨—天與地」) and reconnected with the children. Laughter and joy filled the space, the visit not only brought out smiles, but also sparked immense creativity among the young children.</p>'=>'<p>在6月29日，EJI义工队有幸再次探访播道儿童之家，延续这一温暖传统。 此行我们举办了一场以「<em>我爱水墨—天与地</em>」为主题的<em>水墨画工作坊</em>，与孩子们重聚，展开创作。 这次探访不仅带来笑容，更激发了孩子们无限的创造力。</p>','<p>This year, we proudly announce a significant enhancement to our support for the Evangel Children’s Home. We have committed to being one of the primary donors for the<a href="https://www.ech.org.hk/en/services/day-care-service-sen/"> SEN 3.0 project</a>. This initiative will focus on enhancing daycare services for children with special educational needs (SEN), aiming to provide targeted support that fosters their growth and development in nurturing environments.</p>
<p>Looking ahead, we are excited to continue this heartwarming journey with Evangel Children’s Home, filled with more creativity, commitment, and positive support in the years to come.</p>
<p>We extend our heartfelt thanks to everyone who made this visit a memorable and joyful day!</p>'=>'<p>今年，我们将进一步加强对播道儿童之家的支持， 成为其「<a href="https://www.ech.org.hk/en/services/day-care-service-sen/">SEN 3.0计划</a>」的主要捐助者之一。 这项计划将专注于加强对有特殊教育需要 （SEN） 儿童的日托服务，旨在提供有针对性的支持，促进他们在养育环境中的成长和发展。</p>
<p>展望未来，我们期待与播道儿童之家继续这段温暖旅程；以更多创意、承诺与积极支持，丰富彼此。</p>
<p>我们衷心感谢所有让这次探访难忘和快乐的人！</p>','A Day of Art and Inspiration'=>'艺术与灵感的一天','About Evangel Children’s Home​'=>'关于播道儿童之家','Continuous Support with SEN 3.0'=>'SEN 3.0 的持续支援','Evangel Children’s Home (ECH) was established in 1956 and founded by Ms Ruth Sundquist, an American missionary from the US Evangelical Free Church. ECH has been committed to supporting the healthy growth of orphans, children and youth from broken families or families with difficult backgrounds.'=>'播道儿童之家（ECH）由美国福音自由教会传教士Ruth Sundquist女士于1956年创立，致力于协助孤儿、破碎家庭或背景困难的儿童及青少年健康成长。 ','Read more'=>'阅读更多','description_text-image-box-f5a9acc'=>'播道儿童之家（ECH）由美国福音自由教会传教士Ruth Sundquist女士于1956年创立，致力于协助孤儿、破碎家庭或背景困难的儿童及青少年健康成长。 ','editor-text-editor-199946b'=>'<p><strong><big>关注我们</big></strong></p>','editor-text-editor-29e0b6c'=>'<p>在6月29日，EJI义工队有幸再次探访播道儿童之家，延续这一温暖传统。 此行我们举办了一场以「<em>我爱水墨—天与地</em>」为主题的<em>水墨画工作坊</em>，与孩子们重聚，展开创作。 这次探访不仅带来笑容，更激发了孩子们无限的创造力。</p>','editor-text-editor-b81cfc8'=>'<p>即使工作繁忙，EJI团队始终不忘支援社区的承诺。 我们与<a href="https://www.ech.org.hk/">播道儿童之家</a>的长期合作是这份承诺的核心：支持社会中脆弱的群体——来自困难背景的儿童，是我们作为企业的责任。</p>','editor-text-editor-dc4d231'=>'<p>今年，我们将进一步加强对播道儿童之家的支持， 成为其「<a href="https://www.ech.org.hk/en/services/day-care-service-sen/">SEN 3.0计划</a>」的主要捐助者之一。 这项计划将专注于加强对有特殊教育需要 （SEN） 儿童的日托服务，旨在提供有针对性的支持，促进他们在养育环境中的成长和发展。</p>
<p>展望未来，我们期待与播道儿童之家继续这段温暖旅程；以更多创意、承诺与积极支持，丰富彼此。</p>
<p>我们衷心感谢所有让这次探访难忘和快乐的人！</p>','https://www.ech.org.hk/'=>'https://www.ech.org.hk/','tabs-tab_content-f479391-094376b'=>'<h5><a href="https://x4v3b03dwm-staging.onrocket.site/our-inspiring-visit-to-evangel-childrens-home/">探访播道儿童之家</a></h5>','tabs-tab_title-f479391-094376b'=>'阅读更多','title-heading-0a4699f'=>'SEN 3.0 的持续支援','title-heading-9eca9f0'=>'艺术与灵感的一天','title_text-image-box-f5a9acc'=>'关于播道儿童之家','url-image-box-f5a9acc'=>'https://www.ech.org.hk/']];
